<div id="review_1414250254" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1414250254" />
    <a title="Yevhenii Tseluiko" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/23763578-yevhenii-tseluiko"><img alt="Yevhenii Tseluiko" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1412248626p2/23763578.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1414250254?book_show_action=true">Oct 11, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Yevhenii Tseluiko" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Yevhenii Tseluiko" href="/user/show/23763578-yevhenii-tseluiko">Yevhenii Tseluiko</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
                  <em>
                    This review has been hidden because it contains spoilers. To view it,
                    <a href="#" onclick="Effect.toggle(&#39;reviewTextContainer1414250254&#39;); return false;">click here.</a>
                  </em>
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1414250254" class="readable"
                    style="display:none"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7384661837845921161">Отличная книга о самом скорбном времени в истории России. Формат дневниковых записей еще больше воздействует на читателя, заставляя почувствовать себя очевидцем эпохи. Читать всем, кому интересна тема революции 1917 года и гражданской войны.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

